Detailed Description

cvmx_nqm_vf::_int

This register provides status and clears per-VF interrupts sources. If a bit in this register ANDed with NQM_VF()_INT_ENA_W1C is true then NQM_INTSN_E::NQM_VF()_INT is thrown.
